[1] Norovirus, community & hospital - New Zealand (Dunedin): confirmed
Date: Fri 25 Jun 2004
From: John Holmes <John.Holmes@phsouth.co.nz>

Re: Norovirus, community & hospital based - New Zealand (Dunedin):
suspected [see: Viral gastroenteritis update 2004 (21): part [4]
20040623.1671]
-----------------------
Norovirus has been isolated from specimens. A further 32 staff and 13
patients have been notified as of 1200 NZST 25 Jun 2004.
